<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>8431</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>11574</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>麻雀：呼！这里太热了！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11575</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>15153</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>麻雀：我在这沙漠上飞了一整天了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>15154</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>19239</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>麻雀：我需要一个凉爽的地方来休息。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>19240</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>22005</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>麻雀：看，地上有一个洞。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>22006</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>33935</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>麻雀：我要在这里休息。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>33936</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>37882</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>老鼠：你是谁？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>37883</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>42112</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>麻雀：哦，对不起。我是麻雀。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>42113</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>46322</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>麻雀：沙漠太干燥太炎热了，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>46323</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>51645</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>麻雀：我没想到能在这里看到其他活的动物！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>51646</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>58501</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>老鼠：我是一只沙漠鼠，这里有很多动物。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>58502</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>59800</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>麻雀：真的吗？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>59801</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>66242</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>老鼠：是的。天气很热很干燥，但是晚上很冷。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>66243</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>71033</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>老鼠：所以大部分的动物白天不会活动。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>71034</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>74785</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>麻雀：但你们是如何忍受这高温的？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>74786</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>77465</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>麻雀：我快要热死了！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>77466</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>82946</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>老鼠：一些动物利用他们身体的一部分来降温。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>82947</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>91329</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>老鼠：比如，沙漠里的猫头鹰张大嘴巴，然后震动他们的喉咙。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>91330</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>97668</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>老鼠：长耳大野兔的耳朵很长，而且布满了血管。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>97669</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>102527</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>老鼠：热量通过耳朵上的血管散发出来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>102528</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>105786</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>麻雀：哇，太有趣了！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>105787</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>111209</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>麻雀：在北方，我看过一些耳朵很短的兔子们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>111210</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>117451</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>老鼠：是的，在北方，他们不需要长耳朵来生存。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>117452</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>123223</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>老鼠：世界各地，动物们都适应着各自的生存环境。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>123224</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>128093</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>老鼠：比如，大部分的沙漠动物都是浅色的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>128094</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>133054</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>老鼠：这种浅色也能防止身体温度过高。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>133055</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>136540</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>麻雀：那颜色深一点的动物呢？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>136541</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>141849</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>麻雀：他们比浅色的动物更容易觉得热，是吗？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>141850</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>143312</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>老鼠：你说得对。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>143313</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>150620</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>老鼠：秃鹰就是深色动物，但是他们用尿液把腿弄湿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>150621</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>154330</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>老鼠：尿液会给腿上的血液降温。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>154331</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>158914</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>老鼠：降温后的血液再流回身体里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>158915</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>162584</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>麻雀：我明白了。他们真厉害！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>162585</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>167128</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>麻雀：那沙漠里的动物如何捕食呢？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>167129</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>170040</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>麻雀：你需要水，不是吗？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>170041</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>175888</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>老鼠：当然！我们从植物中摄取水分。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>175889</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>180312</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>老鼠：多汁的仙人掌是我的最爱！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>180313</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>181858</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>老鼠：尝一块吧！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>181859</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>186405</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>麻雀：但是我会不会被刺扎到呢？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>186406</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>192110</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>老鼠：不会的。试一试吧，小心点。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>192111</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>195956</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>麻雀：嗯，不错嘛！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>195957</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>201209</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>麻雀：对了，你在沙漠是如何保持凉爽的？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>201210</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>204470</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>老鼠：我在地下的洞里生活。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>204471</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>208971</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>老鼠：天气太热的时候我就把洞口堵上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>208972</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>213134</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>老鼠：这样就能把热空气阻挡在外面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>213135</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>218868</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>老鼠：然后我就能保存通过呼吸散发出来的水分。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>218869</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>224114</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>麻雀：太棒了！沙漠里的动物真厉害。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>224115</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>228108</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>麻雀：但是我可能无法在这里生存。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>228109</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>232982</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>老鼠：的确如此。沙漠里的降雨很少。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>232983</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>237466</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>老鼠：一年的降雨量不足二十五厘米！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>237467</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>244364</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>老鼠：所以沙漠里所有的动物都有自己独特的生存方法。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>244365</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>246923</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>老鼠：不过你有翅膀。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>246924</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>251606</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>老鼠：你可以飞到一个适合你生存的地方。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>251607</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>254254</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>麻雀：是的，你说得对！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>254255</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>256278</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>麻雀：我现在要走了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>256279</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>260438</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>麻雀：谢谢你告诉我有关沙漠动物的事情。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>260439</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>261590</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>麻雀：再见！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>261591</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>269885</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>老鼠：不用谢！再见！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>